    <title>This new Mac app uses animated flies to tell you when to take out the trash</title>
    <content type="html">  

    &lt;figure&gt;
      &lt;img alt="An image of a macOS dock with the Trash icon surrounded by flies." src="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/xEaPLO3ndn0aR0etZKyTvw6cbqY=/150x0:1512x908/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73436775/Screenshot_2024_06_30_at_4.37.29_PM.0.png" /&gt;
        &lt;figcaption&gt;&lt;em&gt;Buzz buzz.&lt;/em&gt; | Image: Bananbin&lt;/figcaption&gt;
